(102425, 0, 0, 0, 'Beakbuck won\'t let them get close. He\'s such a fine companion.', 64270), -- 102425
(101767, 0, 0, 0, 'They came with superior numbers. How else could they have destroyed us so?', 64270), -- 101767
(99483, 0, 0, 0, 'This is where we remember General Startalon, one of the finest generals our people has ever known. He commanded the Hippogryph riders during the War of the Ancients.$b$bI used to visit his tomb often to meditate for guidance. I wonder if I will see him.', 64270), -- 99483
